sql_query.sql:
SELECT "group_users"."group_id" FROM "group_users" WHERE "group_users"."group_id" IN (SELECT "groups"."id" FROM "groups" WHERE (groups.id > 0) AND ( groups.id IN (
   SELECT id
     FROM groups
    WHERE visibility_level = 0

   UNION ALL

   SELECT id
     FROM groups
    WHERE visibility_level = 1
      AND 1802 IS NOT NULL

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 1802
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 2

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
LEFT JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 1802 AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 3
      AND (gu.id IS NOT NULL OR FALSE)

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 1802 AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 4
 )
) AND (automatic IS FALSE OR groups.id = 2) ORDER BY user_count DESC) AND "group_users"."user_id" = 1802
